to :before/:after. (Using counters in :before/:after is bad.)

Bert added:
| Ad issue 99: ':first-letter' does not match a list markers, but it
| does match whatever is the element's first letter after :before and
| :after have been added. But how about a list marker with
| 'list-style-position: inside'?
 -- http://www.w3.org/mid/16346.1332.851144.151266@lanalana.inria.fr

