   ..."with a marker outside ('list-style-position: outside'), the
   ':first-letter' applies to the principal box of the element, not to
   the marker."
...to:
   ...", the ':first-letter' applies to the first letter in the
   principal box after the marker. UAs may ignore ':first-letter' on
   list items with 'list-style-position: inside'."

