Issue 202. http://www.w3.org/mid/B2901A91-05A3-11D8-A7F5-000A958E6110@apple.com
Does first-line apply to list-items and table-cells as well as blocks?

(Original resolution: Yes, :first-line DOES apply to list-items and
table-cells as well as blocks. The effect of :first-line on list item
markers is undefined in CSS2.1. See
http://tantek.com/w3c/css/litdfirstline.html for tests and results.)
Resolution changed due to issue resolution conflict with issue 219.
Resolution: See issue 219.
Issue closed.
