Issue 274. Fallout from computed/used issue in 4.3.2 Lengths

| Child elements do not inherit the relative values specified for
| their parent; they (generally) inherit the computed values.

Strike "(generally)".

| In cases where the computed length cannot be supported, user agents
| must approximate it in the actual value.

Change "computed" to "used" and linkify.

Resolution: Accepted.
Document updated.
Issue closed.
